You are today 's daily cleaning routine.
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1oFRy9KZS0A_Hd5Py47HxLMCxDhDZW9xZJISUoiHSA18/edit#gid=0

The process is as follows.

Some processes have changed, so be careful with the bold text.

1. On your own time between 5 am and 5 pm
   Immediately prior to the start of the cleaning, inform the manager,
   Hyo jeong, hyojeong5663@gmail.com (offline or online).
   Ventilate by opening windows and doors in big rooms and small rooms,
   At the same time, in a line that does not interfere with the person sitting
   Simply sweep the floor of the open space with a broom.
   If you think it is too cold, you can stop the ventilation before the broom finishes.

2. After completing the cleaning, let the manager (Hyo jeong) know
   the time (from several hours to several minutes) of the cleaning progress.

- Cleaning time is
  Without constraints
  You can do it at your convenience at any time,
  We recommend before / after meals to minimize disruption to the sitting person.
- If someone feels it is too cold due to the ventilation, he/she can ask
  you to stop the ventilation. 
  In this case, you can stop the ventilation immediately if it seems that
  ventilation is somewhat common sense.
- Floor cleaning space is common sense in the line that can minimize the
  interference of the person sitting in the seat,
  In the case of large rooms, only the corridor, in the case of small rooms, it
  is recommended to clean only the space in front of the refrigerator.

Reference: Park Sung Jae

